<title>UK: BOE allots 270 mln stg in outright bills, repo.</title>
<headline>BOE allots 270 mln stg in outright bills, repo.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Bank of England said that it provided the UK money market with 270 million stg of assistance.</p>
<p>It allotted 85 million stg in bills outright and 185 million stg in repos to April 28.</p>
<p>The forecast shortage is 450 million stg.</p>
